Hey there, we have an API for getting all kinds of data like 404s, uptime, cache hits, total requests etc.
<https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/api/cms/performance>

Additionally if you want to fix broken links on your website the SEO recommendations tool in HubSpot automatically finds your broken links and enables you to quickly fix them:
<https://knowledge.HubSpot.com/seo/view-seo-recommendations-in-HubSpot>
